---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';

const title = 'Collectibles Fulfillment | 40-60% Humidity Control, Professional Grading, GPS-Tracked Delivery | MTP';
const description = 'Specialized fulfillment for collectibles, trading cards, figurines, coins, vinyl records. Humidity 40-60%, professional documentation, expert grading, maximum protection, 100% insurance, 24-48 hour delivery.';
const ogImage = 'https://profm.ua/images/fulfillment-collectibles.jpg';

const schema = {
  '@context': 'https://schema.org',
  '@type': 'Service',
  name: title,
  description: description,
  provider: {
    '@type': 'Organization',
    name: 'MTP Group',
    url: 'https://profm.ua/en/'
  },
  areaServed: {
    '@type': 'Country',
    name: 'UA'
  },
  priceRange: '₴500-₴1000'
};
---

<Base title={title} description={description} ogImage={ogImage} lang="en">
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-red-600 to-red-500 text-white py-16 sm:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold mb-6 leading-tight">
        Collectibles Fulfillment<br />Museum-Grade Storage, Professional Grading, Specialized Delivery
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl mb-8 opacity-95 leading-relaxed">
        Trading cards, coins, figurines, vinyl records, memorabilia. Perfect humidity 40-60%, 18-22°C climate control, professional photo documentation, expert grading, maximum protection, 100% insurance, GPS-tracked delivery.
      </p>
      <a href="#contact" class="inline-block bg-white text-red-600 px-8 py-4 rounded font-bold text-lg hover:bg-gray-100 transition">
        Start Collectibles Fulfillment
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">Why Collectibles Need Specialized Fulfillment</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">💎 Extreme Value &amp; Risk</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Rare cards worth 100,000+ UAH, vintage coins 50,000+ UAH. Loss of one item = major financial damage. Requires maximum security and zero-loss protocols.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">🔍 Climate-Sensitive Storage</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Cards warp with humidity changes. Coins rust above 60% humidity. Vinyl warps at temperature swings. Requires stable 40-60% humidity, 18-22°C constant control.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">📸 Professional Documentation</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Collectors demand proof of condition. Professional photos from all angles. Expert grading (mint, near-mint, excellent). Complete chain-of-custody documentation.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">🤝 Collector Experience</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Collectors value details and transparency. Requires attentive handling, clear communication, visible care. White-glove treatment expected.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

\1  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">How MTP Group Handles Collectibles Orders</h2>
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none mb-12">
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
          With 10 years of experience in specialized fulfillment and over 150 active clients, MTP Group has optimized every step of order processing. Our 3,900 m² warehouse is purpose-built for high-velocity fulfillment across diverse categories.
        </p>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">The Fulfillment Challenge</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
          Collectible retailers deal with high-value items—action figures, trading cards, vintage items—each requiring careful handling. Customers expect pristine condition on arrival. Damage eliminates entire order value.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
          MTP Group's approach: Collectibles are stored individually in protective cases, organized by category. Staff wear gloves and use careful handling protocols. Each item is wrapped in acid-free tissue and placed in custom boxes. We photograph items before shipping for documentation.
        </p>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Why Retailers Choose MTP</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          Collectible margins are 40–60% but damage reduces value by 50–100%. Our protective packing and damage-free delivery preserve full customer satisfaction and repeat purchases.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          MTP Group has processed <strong>9,000+ collectible orders processed, 22+ specialty retailers served</strong>. Our experience in this category translates to faster integration, fewer picking errors, and predictable costs.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

   Collectibles Services</h2>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">✓ Museum-Grade Climate Control</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Dedicated collectibles vault: 40-60% humidity, 18-22°C constant temperature. Hourly sensor monitoring. Dedicated climate zone isolation. Complete environmental logging.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">✓ Professional Photo Documentation</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">All angles photographed. Detailed condition description. Professional grading assessment. Comprehensive documentation with official seal and signature.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">✓ Maximum Protection Packaging</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Cards in protective sleeves, then foam-lined boxes. Coins in capsules, then rigid cases. Multi-layer shock absorption. Custom protective structures per item type.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">✓ Specialized Courier Delivery</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Premium collectibles via specialized courier. Real-time GPS tracking. Before/after photos. Chain-of-custody documentation. Insured transportation.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">Pricing for Collectibles</h2>
      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border border-gray-200 mb-8">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-4">Fulfillment &amp; Documentation</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
          <li class="flex justify-between">
            <span>Handling &amp; packaging per item</span>
            <span class="font-bold">50–150 UAH</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex justify-between">
            <span>Professional photo &amp; documentation</span>
            <span class="font-bold">100–300 UAH</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex justify-between">
            <span>Expert grading (optional)</span>
            <span class="font-bold">200–500 UAH</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex justify-between">
            <span>Climate-controlled storage per pallet/month</span>
            <span class="font-bold">+100 UAH</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex justify-between">
            <span>Specialized courier delivery</span>
            <span class="font-bold">300–600 UAH</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex justify-between">
            <span>100% insurance coverage</span>
            <span class="font-bold">Included</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-red-50 p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
        <h3 class="font-bold mb-3">Example: Collectibles Trading Platform (100 orders/month)</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          Handling &amp; packaging: 100 × 100 = 10,000 UAH<br/>
          Photo documentation: 100 × 200 = 20,000 UAH<br/>
          Specialized delivery: 100 × 450 = 45,000 UAH<br/>
          <strong class="text-lg">TOTAL: 75,000 UAH/month = 750 UAH per order</strong><br/>
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-600">Includes: 40-60% humidity control, professional grading, maximum protection, GPS-tracked delivery, 100% insurance</span>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">Collector Protection Guarantees</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="text-center bg-white p-6 rounded border border-green-200">
          <p class="text-4xl font-bold text-green-600 mb-2">40–60%</p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 font-bold">Humidity Control</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-2">Museum-grade preservation</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center bg-white p-6 rounded border border-green-200">
          <p class="text-4xl font-bold text-green-600 mb-2">Professional</p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 font-bold">Grading & Documentation</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-2">Expert condition assessment</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center bg-white p-6 rounded border border-green-200">
          <p class="text-4xl font-bold text-green-600 mb-2">100%</p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 font-bold">Insured Delivery</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-2">GPS-tracked, immediate claims</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">Why Fulfillment Speed & Accuracy Matter for Your Business</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">⏱️ Speed = Competitive Advantage</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">E-commerce customers expect 24-48 hour delivery. Slow fulfillment leads to lost orders and negative reviews. MTP Group's 2-4 hour order processing means your customers receive tracking updates the same day they order. This builds trust and encourages repeat purchases. Faster fulfillment also reduces storage costs by turning inventory quickly.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">✅ Accuracy = Customer Retention</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Wrong item? The customer will return it, costing you both labor and shipping. Wrong quantity? Dispute and potential chargeback. Our 99.95%+ accuracy means customers receive exactly what they ordered—building satisfaction and driving 30-40% repeat order rates. Happy customers become your marketing channel through word-of-mouth and reviews.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">💰 Margins Are Everything</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Fulfillment is often 10-20% of your total order cost. Partner with a provider who understands your margin structure and helps you optimize every step. MTP Group's transparent pricing and category expertise mean you pay only for what you use, with no hidden fees. Our 10 years of experience has helped 150+ retailers identify cost-saving opportunities.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">🔄 Scaling Without Stress</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Black Friday. Holiday season. New product launch. These peak periods either make or break your year. You need a fulfillment partner who scales with you—not one that delays orders during your busiest time. MTP Group guarantees 2-3x capacity scaling on 7 days' notice, ensuring your customers always get on-time delivery even during peak volume.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-gradient-to-r from-red-600 to-red-500 text-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Ready to Protect Your Collectibles Platform?</h2>
      <p class="text-xl mb-8 opacity-90">
        Museum-grade climate control, professional documentation, expert grading, maximum protection, GPS-tracked delivery, 100% insurance. Start today.
      </p>
      <a href="#contact" class="inline-block bg-white text-red-600 px-8 py-4 rounded font-bold text-lg hover:bg-gray-100 transition">
        Request a Quote
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(schema)}></script>
</Base>
